# Webhook reference docs (moved out of CMB form, below Save button)
msgid "Webhook reference & response codes"
msgstr "Webhook-reference & svar-koder"

msgid "How to configure webhooks at Økoskabet"
msgstr "Sådan konfigurerer du webhooks hos Økoskabet"

msgid "Log in to Økoskabet's dashboard."
msgstr "Log ind på Økoskabets dashboard."

msgid "Navigate to webhook settings."
msgstr "Gå til webhook-indstillingerne."

msgid "For EACH merchant configured here, register a separate webhook in Økoskabet with its merchant-specific URL (shown next to each merchant in the table above) and the matching webhook secret you saved on the merchant record. Each merchant has its own signing secret — never share a secret across merchants."
msgstr "For HVER merchant konfigureret her, registrér en separat webhook hos Økoskabet med dens merchant-specifikke URL (vist ved hver merchant i tabellen ovenfor) og det matchende webhook secret du har gemt på merchanten. Hver merchant har sin egen signing secret — del aldrig en secret på tværs af merchants."

msgid "Register a webhook in Økoskabet pointing at <code>%s</code> with Method <code>POST</code>, Content-Type <code>application/json</code>, and the signing secret you set in the Webhook Secret field above."
msgstr "Registrér en webhook hos Økoskabet der peger på <code>%s</code> med Method <code>POST</code>, Content-Type <code>application/json</code> og det signing secret du har sat i Webhook Secret-feltet ovenfor."

msgid "Select the events you want Økoskabet to send — typically:"
msgstr "Vælg de events du vil have Økoskabet til at sende — typisk:"

msgid "Only events you have ticked under \"Capture events\" or \"Completion events\" trigger any action — the rest are accepted and ignored."
msgstr "Kun events du har markeret under \"Capture-events\" eller \"Completion-events\" udløser en handling — resten accepteres og ignoreres."

msgid "Expected payload format"
msgstr "Forventet payload-format"

msgid "The plugin maps Økoskabet's \"reservation_updated\" event into the internal events shown in the settings above (in_shed, order_delivered) by inspecting the \"changes\" payload."
msgstr "Plugin'et oversætter Økoskabets \"reservation_updated\"-event til de interne events vist i indstillingerne ovenfor (in_shed, order_delivered) ved at inspicere \"changes\"-payloaden."

msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "Autentificering"

msgid "Each webhook is verified by an HMAC-SHA256 signature of the raw request body, using the merchant's webhook secret. Økoskabet computes the signature on its side and sends it as the lowercase hex value of this header:"
msgstr "Hver webhook verificeres med en HMAC-SHA256 signatur over selve request-body'en, ved brug af merchantens webhook secret. Økoskabet beregner signaturen på deres side og sender den som lowercase hex-værdi i denne header:"

msgid "If the header is missing, malformed, or does not match, the request is rejected with HTTP 401. The <strong>API key</strong> field is NOT used to authenticate webhooks — it's only used for outbound API calls to Økoskabet."
msgstr "Hvis headeren mangler, er ugyldig eller ikke matcher, afvises requesten med HTTP 401. <strong>API-nøgle</strong>-feltet bruges IKKE til at autentificere webhooks — den bruges kun til udgående API-kald til Økoskabet."

msgid "Test a webhook locally with curl"
msgstr "Test en webhook lokalt med curl"

msgid "Response codes"
msgstr "Svar-koder"

msgid "webhook processed."
msgstr "webhook behandlet."

msgid "invalid or missing HMAC signature."
msgstr "ugyldig eller manglende HMAC-signatur."

msgid "webhook functionality is disabled in plugin settings, OR the order belongs to a different merchant than the one in the webhook URL."
msgstr "webhook-funktionalitet er slået fra i plugin-indstillingerne, ELLER ordren tilhører en anden merchant end den i webhook-URL'en."

msgid "the merchant ID in the URL is unknown, OR the order referenced by shipment_reference does not exist."
msgstr "merchant-ID'et i URL'en er ukendt, ELLER ordren der refereres af shipment_reference findes ikke."

msgid "the merchant has no webhook secret configured. Edit the merchant and paste a value."
msgstr "merchanten har ingen webhook secret konfigureret. Rediger merchanten og indsæt en værdi."

msgid "WooCommerce is not loaded."
msgstr "WooCommerce er ikke indlæst."

msgid "Success response example"
msgstr "Eksempel på success-response"
